author: Robert Barnes
title: Supreme Court rules for Republicans over Wisconsin vote, highlighting partisan divide before November poll
description: Conservative majority prevails in the fight between Republicans and Democrats on the issue of extending absentee balloting.
content:
Just the caption of the case Republican National Committee v. Democratic National Committee was foreboding for a Supreme Court that likes to cast itself as above partisan politics.
